Mage Relm: This outfit that causes a personality change is
probably a special one with a demon's name attached to it.

san always takes on troublesome requests...

you know!

Priestess Sophia: Mmmph... Puff...! They said that all the
pursuers have been defeated.
Priestess Sophia: We can't let our guard down either.

Clea: Let's explore the cave. We'll decide what to do once
we find Eisa-san.
